  "original_title": "Lanka IOC signs agreement with Spectrum Trading",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Lanka IOC signs agreement with Spectrum Trading",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "LIOC Managing Director Manoj Gupta (seated left) along with Spectrum Trading Co. Managing Director",
        "Dr. Kalinga Kaluperuma and senior officials during the agreement signing",
        "Lanka IOC, Sri Lanka\u2019s No. 1 listed energy company has joined hands with the prestigious Stafford Group for the supply of co-branded SERVO ecoPLUS \u2013 a long life and eco-friendly lubricant to its dealers\u2019 network for the first time in Sri Lanka.",
        "LIOC manufactures automotive, industrial and marine SERVO lubricants at its state-of-art plant in Trincomalee.",
        "In a statement LIOC affirmed its commitment to the development and economy of Sri Lanka. The entire range of SERVO Lubricants is locally manufactured, thus saving precious foreign exchange on imports.",
        "The company has always been at the forefront of offering the best quality lubricants at competitive prices. Besides this, LIOC will be the only company to set up a grease manufacturing plant in Sri Lanka.",
        "Spectrum Trading Co. Ltd., a leader in the marketing and distribution of automotive products is a member of the diversified Stafford Group.",
        "The first co-branded lubricant of LIOC has been launched as \u2018SERVO ecoPLUS\u2019 meeting API SN, the highest performance level specified by American Petroleum Institute. SERVO ecoPLUS is an eco-friendly, fuel-efficient, affordable long life lubricant which gives shield protection for the vehicle."
      ],
